The Data

We work with two dataframes of the following data:

  • Crop historical data: agr_df
  • Price series (corn): corn_df

Crop data

First we will explore the crop data to identify different characteristics of agriculture in Mexico in the years 2003-2020.

The data can be found in the official website of SIAP: http://infosiap.siap.gob.mx/gobmx/datosAbiertos.php
